### Link to this sectionHow do I convert a COCO dataset to the YOLO format?#

You can convert a COCO dataset to the YOLO format using the [Ultralytics conversion tools](/reference/data/converter). Here's a quick method:
    
    
    from ultralytics.data.converter import convert_coco
    
    convert_coco(labels_dir="path/to/coco/annotations/")

This code will convert your COCO annotations to YOLO format, enabling seamless integration with Ultralytics YOLO models. For additional details, visit the Port or Convert Label Formats section.

